{"tid":510131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"赤腳上身闖聖伯多祿廣場搶聖嬰　女權主義者高呼「上帝是女人」","createTime":"2017-12-26T07:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T15:38:48.000Z","uid":42188,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"8c42eaec80a1da33d3f158847749b96f7580ec66","tid":510131,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:04:21.000Z","msg":"聖誕文告前夕，一名女權組織費曼（Femen）的成員，突然闖入梵蒂岡聖伯多祿廣場，搶走嬰兒耶穌雕像，並高呼「上帝是女人」。 該名赤裸上身的Femen成員，當刻跳過圍欄，試圖在聖伯多祿廣場的耶誕誕生佈景中，奪走一尊聖嬰的雕像，她除了高呼「上帝是女人」之外，背部亦劃上是「God is Woman」字句，該名女子隨即被制伏。<br />\n<br />\nFemen為烏克蘭的女權組織，成立於2008年，目標是擊敗父權。Femen指該名示威者為一名性別極端份子，而今次行動目的，是為了透過綁架宗教團體的嬰孩象徵，去展示女性自主。"},{"pid":"3096b5c2c9414a7233d0d42154e8d121ca5e8060","tid":510131,"uid":67684,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:06:42.000Z","msg":"女權撚真係柒少一日都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876978de15b148ab703c5a753f4550626afd3b1c","tid":510131,"uid":8048,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:11:16.000Z","msg":"挑戰神聖不可侵犯的耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好睇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e62899682d6f2fddc452e7ef5d5408eee9bf74","tid":510131,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8523dc3635809a73299c700fc46702ddb782f16","tid":510131,"uid":26752,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:15:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">女權閪係夠膽既就話真神阿拉係女人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n耶教上帝同真神阿拉都係同一個神<br />\n女權閪有膽搞耶撚冇膽搞班蛔<br />\n欺善怕惡垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"af6e50151998da9bea73dba039c67bf6c782350b","tid":510131,"uid":62815,"like"